  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed extension, by reason of its inappropriate design, scale, massing, height and siting is considered to form an incongruous and discordant feature when seen from the public and private realm.  The proposal would have an adverse visual impact on the character and appearance of the host property, the wider terrace and the Conservation Area, with no public benefit to outweigh this harm.  The proposal is therefore contrary to the NPPF 2021, policies D3, D4 and HC1 of the London Plan 2021, policies CS8 and CS9 of the Core Strategy (2011), policies DM2.1 and DM2.3 of the Development Management Policies (2013) and the guidance in the Islington Urban Design Guide (2017) and Conservation Area Design Guidelines."
